Package honeyroasted.jype.system

Class TypeSystem

java.lang.Object
honeyroasted.jype.system.TypeSystem
public class TypeSystem extends Object
This class represents a type system, along with a TypeCache. It allows creation of types from reflection values and TypeMirror values (for annotation processing). Additionally, it provides standard types such as NULL, all the primitives, their boxes, and the OBJECT class.
